OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FA retreat owner who fled the country
OL,7,Fafter throwing a corrosive chemical
OL,8,Fonto a guest's face, has been jailed.
OL,10,FDean Mayze, 38, was discovered in
OL,11,FRomania, almost three years after the
OL,12,Fincident at Hafan y Coed in Abercraf.
OL,14,FA sentencing hearing at Swansea Crown
OL,15,FCourt heard how on 10 December 2022,
OL,16,FMayze threw a corrosive substance on
OL,17,FKiefer Price.
