OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FGeorgia Donohue, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fcourt how Mr Price had been a guest at
OL,8,Fthe retreat and was renting a room
OL,9,Fthere at the time.
OL,11,FMs Donohue said Mr Price had become
OL,12,Funhappy with the state of his room -
OL,13,Fit did not have proper bathing
OL,14,Ffacilities or heating so Mr Price
OL,15,Fchose to leave the room and cancel his
OL,16,Frental standard order.
