OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FMr Price then went to retrieve his
OL,7,Fbikes from the store cupboard at the
OL,8,Fsite but found the door had been
OL,9,Flocked with his property inside. He
OL,10,Fmessaged Mayze on social media to ask
OL,11,Fwhy it was locked but his message was
OL,12,Fignored, Ms Donohue said.
OL,14,FMr Price then kicked the door of the
OL,15,Fshed down to access his bikes and
OL,16,Fbegan taking them to his van. When he
OL,17,Freturned to collect his final bike he
OL,18,Fwas confronted by Mayze and his son.
