OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FMayze was angry and asked him why he
OL,7,Fhad kicked the door down, before
OL,8,Fmoving towards Mr Price and throwing a
OL,9,Fblue container at him.
OL,11,FLiquid poured out of the container and
OL,12,Fwent on the guest's face, up his nose
OL,13,Fand in both of his eyes. Mr Price
OL,14,Fbegan struggling to breathe and felt
OL,15,F"like his eyes were exploding".
