OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FMayze's partner then drove Mr Price to
OL,7,Fa nearby A&E department where it was
OL,8,Fconfirmed he had suffered chemical
OL,9,Finjuries to both of his eyes. He
OL,10,Fneeded an "intensive course of
OL,11,Ftreatment" in order to stop him from
OL,12,Flosing his eyesight completely.
OL,14,FMs Donohue told the court how two days
OL,15,Flater police went to Mayze's address
OL,16,Fand he was not there. Mayze contacted
OL,17,Fthe police directly and told them he
OL,18,Fhad been at the rugby club all
OL,19,Fweekend. However bank data confirmed
OL,20,Fhis card was being used in Swindon and
OL,21,FHampshire, the court heard.
