OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FIt was then used at Dublin Airport
OL,7,Fbefore he travelled to France, Italy
OL,8,Fand Croatia.
OL,10,FMayze failed to attend a voluntary
OL,11,Fpolice interview and then travelled to
OL,12,FGreece. At the end of January 2023 he
OL,13,Fmessaged police saying he did not need
OL,14,Fto be arrested because his partner had
OL,15,Fhanded herself in.
OL,17,FIt was another two-and-a-half years
OL,18,Flater, in July 2025, that an
OL,19,Fextradition warrant was granted for
OL,20,Fhis arrest for where he then was - in
OL,21,FRomania.
