OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FHe was in custody in a Romanian prison
OL,7,Fbefore being transferred to HMP
OL,8,FWormwood Scrubs and finally Swansea
OL,9,FPrison.
OL,11,FAndrew Taylor, representing Mayze,
OL,12,Fexplained that while in custody in
OL,13,FRomania, Mayze had caught scabies but
OL,14,Fbecause he could not pay for it he was
OL,15,Fgiven no treatment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
