OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FMr Taylor said his client had been
OL,7,Fdescribed as the "model prisoner" and
OL,8,Fsaid he was an intelligent and
OL,9,Fhardworking individual who "wants to
OL,10,Fmake something of himself".
OL,12,FHe called it an "unusual case",
OL,13,Foutlining how his client had been in
OL,14,Fthree different prisons. He added that
OL,15,FMr Price is a "bigger and stronger"
OL,16,Fman than Mayze and described their
OL,17,Frelationship as "tumultous",
OL,18,Femphasising the fact his door had just
OL,19,Fbeen kicked down.
