OL,3,CRetreat owner threw chemical at
OL,4,Cguest's face before fleeing the country
OL,6,FThe court heard that Mayze has four
OL,7,Fprevious convictions for four
OL,8,Foffences. This included a relevant
OL,9,Fwounding offence in 2013 where he had
OL,10,Fthrown a corrosive liquid into
OL,11,Fsomeone's face on a night out.
OL,13,FMayze, of Abercraf in Powys, pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to inflicting grievous bodily
OL,15,Fharm. During sentencing judge Geraint
OL,16,FWalters said it was a "particularly
OL,17,Fwicked way" of inciting violence.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
