OL,6,FJudge Walters sentenced Mayze to 18
OL,7,Fmonths in prison for one count of
OL,8,Fcausing grievous bodily harm and
OL,9,Fordered a restraining order preventing
OL,10,FMayze from approaching the victim for
OL,11,Fa period of three years.
